            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>bashed cucumber</strong> to a medium bowl with the<strong> salad</strong></p><p>Squeeze the juice of your<strong> lemon[s]</strong> over the top with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> and toss together – this is your<strong> zingy salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
